
{center}
{subhead} Innovative AMIGA Newsletter 1/2000{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

As every month, here is our newsletter with the latest news from Innovative
(all news from our main-news-page at {link http://www.innovative-web.de/}http://www.innovative-web.de/{end})
{p} {p}
13.1.2000{p}
{bold}The fourth version is available - VLRec NG 4.0!{nobold}{p}
VLRec NG 4.0 comes with many new features. Among the overworked GUI-graphics in
GlowIcons-style and the enhanced recording-facilities in different sizes, there
is now also a direct link to fxPAINT. Furthermore the speed of VLRec NG was improved
and new effects were added: A must-have for every owner of a VHI-compatible board!
{p} {p}
{bold}fxPAINT-Website updated{nobold}{p}
The website of fxPAINT has been updated and extended. You can now find up-to-date
screenshots and an overview over most of the effects fxPAINT offers to you.
Furthermore the design of the site has been unified and it is navigatable even
better.
{p} {p}
{bold}The first VHI-developer-informations are available{nobold}{p}
Developers can now download the FD-, Include- and Autodoc-file for VHI. An example-
driver with sourceocode and the vhimaster.library will delay until mid of year 2000.
{p} {p}
{bold}VHI-driver for Masoboshi MVD 819 available{nobold}{p}
A VHI-driver for the MVD 819-digitizer is available for free download from the VHI-page.
Best experienced with VLRec NG 4.0 :)
{p} {p}
{bold}innovative-web.de has moved{nobold}{p}
Our website has successfully moved to a faster server. Many additions have been made
while moving: When ordering you can see the p & p, that is added now, too as well as
a short description of the article. Furthermore the navigationbar has been overworked
and the site is now also navigatable in 800x600 without scrolling the bar.